# Pipeline conventions

Read [IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md](IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md) before any pipeline changes.

## State machine

`RAW → PARSED → DIFFED → SUMMARIZED` — each stage idempotent per `rcept_no`.

## Rules

- Raw XML stays in `data/` filesystem, never in MySQL
- LLM input = diffs and extracted facts only, never full filing text
- All outputs must mechanically cite source sections (`FilingExcerptRef`)
- QoQ baseline = prior filing; YoY = same quarter prior year
- Record model/tokens/cost per LLM call

## Scripts

- Manual: `scripts/{stage}_*.py --stock <ticker>`
- Cron: `run_daily_scan.py` (no Gemini), `run_llm_worker.py` (on-demand queue)

## Do not

- Add HTTP endpoints — this repo is CLI + cron only
- Touch `disclosure` / `ai_summary_result` tables (수시공시 = darfin-disclosure)
- Change output shapes without updating `types.js`
